{"tid":348761,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"又邊個巴打要俾人炒","createTime":"2017-08-06T04:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T16:35:16.000Z","uid":3220,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4472e4f1da342f3917c006e54a01f801de0c7e7","tid":348761,"uid":3220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T04:06:30.000Z","msg":"長洲避風塘以北及喜靈洲一帶出現大片油污，避風塘內有油污味，據船家稱，今日已見大量死魚，恐有生態災難，有漁民透露，可能丫洲對出知洲島疑貨船漏油事件，據了解，漏出9000多噸棕櫚油。<br />\n<br />\n康文署宣佈，由於在離島區的洪聖爺灣泳灘、蘆鬚城泳灘、貝澳泳灘、上長沙泳灘、下長沙泳灘及塘福泳灘發現油污，該些泳灘已暫時封閉，並已懸掛紅旗，市民請勿在該處游泳，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170806&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57047420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170806%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57047420&d=85LsdYHTUHxkbjS562haYb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=713993a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170806%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57047420&h=b4936b3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170806&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57047420</a><br />\n【油污襲離島】疑貨船漏油  6泳灘緊急封閉<br />\n<br />\n又邊個入錯油，累成條team 俾人炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b861fd816eb2cf2038eb60567f28c6073c30e3","tid":348761,"uid":3220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:36:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"11a9880eb2e88c1ebc5598c98302c2ccc62fd09b","tid":348761,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"而家咁多新會員 邊有人知你講緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0ad68563608c90114b2145d4e8821a9800bbf7","tid":348761,"uid":56878,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家咁多新會員 邊有人知你講緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />